 freshmeat nebulus
      desc 'OpenGL/SDL visual plugin for XMMS
xmms-nebulus is an OpenGL/SDL visual plugin for XMMS.
It features a lot of options, including fullscreen mode, 
effects priorities, and more.
It requires 3D Hardware Acceleration in order to work.'
